The '''[[Yinchorri/Legends|Yinchorri]] religion''' focused largely on legends of a spirit realm and of ancient myths. One such myth was that there was a spirit world that existed inside the real world; it was termed "[[Uhanayih|Within World]]." Given the Yinchorri attitudes their religion presumably encouraged discovery, expansion, and aggression.

